{"tid":2036752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[係門口] 向中國亮劍！美軍2轟炸機、加油機經台周邊　一度接近香港","createTime":"2020-05-26T15:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T12:56:59.000Z","uid":51620,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdcdac23d724e542d39bb8c9e288535f92b68c3","tid":2036752,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjyrc0F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbjyrc0F.gif&h=81cd26f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美、中兩國近期在台灣附近及南海的軍事動作頻頻，美軍更是頻繁出動素有「死亡天鵝」之稱的B-1B超音速轟炸機巡弋西太平洋，今（26）日美軍再次派出同機型的2架B-1B超音速轟炸機飛經南海，原因為何引發關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/26/2574426-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F2574426-XXL.jpg&h=f1955d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美軍機經南海，一度靠近香港周邊。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n根據「飛機守望」（Aircraft Spots）推特表示，美國空軍2架B-1B超音速戰略轟炸機與一架KC-135R空中加油機，今日自關島安德森空軍基地出發，前往台灣周邊的南海空域執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n有關美軍B-1B轟炸機近期頻繁飛抵台灣周邊空域，美軍此舉是否有特殊暗示意義？我空軍參謀長鄭榮豐日前曾透露，根據判斷美軍相關舉措是一個動態兵力運作模式，有戰略意義在其中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/26/2574440-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F2574440-XXL.jpg&h=be4d2775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美軍機經南海，一度靠近香港周邊。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n此外，從另一張曝光的路線圖顯示，美軍KC-135加油機一度飛近香港，是否和近期中共強推「港版國安法」有關，引發各界關注。由於，明（27）日香港立法會將恢復二讀《國歌條例草案》，加上中國人大將通過《國安法》草案並納入《基本法》附件三在港實施，整個香港緊張情勢進一步升高，美軍機此一敏感時機飛經周邊，也頗有恫嚇中國當局的意味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/26/2574488-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F2574488-XXL.jpg&h=22fbe870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美軍機經南海，一度靠近香港周邊。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=749455&amp;fbclid=IwAR1pjj8WwL11YkAj8KHKhX_tYxvsp5bTFZRvwlzVKLbCAt5lxe9KZWYrJ5U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D749455%26fbclid%3DIwAR1pjj8WwL11YkAj8KHKhX_tYxvsp5bTFZRvwlzVKLbCAt5lxe9KZWYrJ5U&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=8f6b15ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D749455%26fbclid%3DIwAR1pjj8WwL11YkAj8KHKhX_tYxvsp5bTFZRvwlzVKLbCAt5lxe9KZWYrJ5U&h=36b5eafb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=749455&amp;fbclid=IwAR1pjj8WwL11YkAj8KHKhX_tYxvsp5bTFZRvwlzVKLbCAt5lxe9KZWYrJ5U</a>"},{"pid":"835ec2fc9cfd55794a16aa14380048a4fe0587f6","tid":2036752,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993c9f2f85798625cc2c2eeb370c1e1388e89cca","tid":2036752,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaca726ae3281fb560e95212bf8a10cd6628304","tid":2036752,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318cca715a03e788d0c184ffdf7